Unlike other black and white photo apps, this app includes an infrared option that sometimes yields surprising contrast results.  Infrared film was notoriously cumbersome to work with because one can only load a camera with this type of film in total darkness.  This photo app eliminates this problem completely and allows the photographer a host of contrast options that regular black and white film can never deliver.
